NATE, I HAVE TO SAY,

10:21.371 --> 10:23.457
OF ALL THE DECEITFUL,

10:21.371 --> 10:23.457
UNPRINCIPLED,

10:23.498 --> 10:25.208
CORRUPT THINGS I'VE DONE

10:23.498 --> 10:25.208
IN MY ENTIRE LIFE,

10:25.250 --> 10:26.334
NOTHING IS AS BAD AS...

10:26.376 --> 10:27.668
-POLITICS.

10:26.376 --> 10:27.668
-I CAN'T EVEN SAY IT.

10:27.710 --> 10:30.505
ANNOUNCING

10:27.710 --> 10:30.505
YOUR INDEPENDENT CANDIDATE,

10:30.547 --> 10:32.215
MICHAEL VITTORI!

10:32.257 --> 10:33.674
[ APPLAUSE, FEEDBACK SQUEAKS ]

10:33.716 --> 10:35.510
GOOD EVE--

10:35.552 --> 10:36.886
THANK YOU,

10:35.552 --> 10:36.886
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,

10:36.928 --> 10:39.347
FOR BEING HERE TODAY.

10:39.389 --> 10:41.182
OKAY, HOPEFULLY,

10:39.389 --> 10:41.182
VITTORI IS A STALL.

10:41.224 --> 10:42.725
ELIOT, DID YOU FIND

10:41.224 --> 10:42.725
YOUR FRIEND YET?

10:42.767 --> 10:44.311
-Yeah.

10:42.767 --> 10:44.311
-Good.

10:44.352 --> 10:46.187
NO, FLORES ISN'T

10:44.352 --> 10:46.187
IN A REGULAR PRISON.

10:46.229 --> 10:47.272
HE'S IN THE TOMBS --

10:47.314 --> 10:49.232
CELLS UNDERNEATH

10:47.314 --> 10:49.232
THE PARLIAMENT BUILDING,

10:49.274 --> 10:51.151
LEFT OVER

10:49.274 --> 10:51.151
FROM THE OLD COLONIAL DAYS.

10:53.987 --> 10:56.072
THEY TORE THE STAIRWELL OUT,

10:56.114 --> 10:57.198
PUT IN A SINGLE ELEVATOR.

10:57.240 --> 10:59.033
CLOSED SHAFTS, NO ACCESS.

10:59.075 --> 11:00.619
ONLY WAY IN AND OUT.

11:03.371 --> 11:05.499
AND EVEN IF YOU GET PAST

11:03.371 --> 11:05.499
THE GUARDS,

11:05.540 --> 11:08.001
THEY'RE GONNA SHOOT THE ELEVATOR

11:05.540 --> 11:08.001
UP ON YOUR WAY BACK OUT.

11:08.042 --> 11:09.377
IT'S A KILL BOX.

11:09.419 --> 11:11.754
FLORES -- GETTING HIM OUT

11:09.419 --> 11:11.754
IS GONNA BE LOUD.

11:11.796 --> 11:12.797
IT'S GONNA BE MESSY.

11:12.839 --> 11:13.840
HEY, HOW ABOUT THIS?

11:13.881 --> 11:15.509
-STEAM VENT...

11:13.881 --> 11:15.509
[ CLANKS ]

11:15.550 --> 11:17.427
...WELDED SHUT.

11:17.469 --> 11:19.220
IT'S A STEAM VENT, PARKER.

11:19.262 --> 11:20.930
ALL RIGHT?

11:19.262 --> 11:20.930
PEOPLE DON'T --

11:20.972 --> 11:23.141
NORMAL PEOPLE DON'T G--

11:23.183 --> 11:26.811
YOU -- THEY FEEL LIKE --

11:23.183 --> 11:26.811
IT WILL BURN Y--

11:26.853 --> 11:28.438
THIS IS IT.

11:26.853 --> 11:28.438
WE'RE HERE.

11:28.480 --> 11:30.982
THIS INTERSECTION

11:28.480 --> 11:30.982
IS 60 FEET BELOW THE STREET.

11:31.024 --> 11:33.443
YOU SURE THAT'S 60 FEET DOWN?

11:33.485 --> 11:37.364
-♪ AHH ♪

11:33.485 --> 11:37.364
-[ Echoing ]

11:37.405 --> 11:39.366
YEAH. THAT'S IT.

11:37.405 --> 11:39.366
60 FEET.

11:39.407 --> 11:41.742
THAT PIPE.

11:41.784 --> 11:43.786
[ WRENCH SCRAPES ]

11:45.455 --> 11:46.789
BUT WHAT I CAN DO...

11:46.831 --> 11:50.293
IS BE A LIGHT THAT LEADS US

11:46.831 --> 11:50.293
THROUGH THESE DARK DAYS.

11:50.335 --> 11:52.962
MY GRANDMOTHER...

11:53.004 --> 11:56.132
USED TO SAY

11:53.004 --> 11:56.132
THAT THE TRUTH IS A LIGHT,

11:56.174 --> 11:58.259
AND THAT LIGHT MUST SHINE.

11:58.301 --> 12:01.513
LET ME LIGHT THE WAY

11:58.301 --> 12:01.513
FOR SAN LORENZO,

12:01.555 --> 12:02.681
AND, IN TURN...

12:04.891 --> 12:08.144
...OUR SMALL ISLAND --

12:08.186 --> 12:10.605
LITTLE BODY

12:08.186 --> 12:10.605
WITH A MIGHTY HEART --

12:10.647 --> 12:12.273
WILL BE A LIGHT

12:10.647 --> 12:12.273
THAT LEADS THE WORLD.

12:12.315 --> 12:13.732
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

12:17.362 --> 12:19.030
-MR. VITTORI...

12:19.072 --> 12:20.781
WHAT ARE YOUR THOUGHTS

12:19.072 --> 12:20.781
ABOUT THE WORLD ECONOMY?

12:20.823 --> 12:22.492
HOW DO YOU FEEL ABOUT

12:20.823 --> 12:22.492
SAN LORENZO JOINING NATO?

12:22.534 --> 12:24.160
WHAT ABOUT THE WHEREABOUTS

12:24.202 --> 12:25.453
OF GENERAL FLORES?

12:25.495 --> 12:27.872
HA! LOOK AT HIM RUN.

12:27.914 --> 12:30.166
NO, THAT SPEECH WAS VERY ODD.

12:30.208 --> 12:33.169
IT WAS GOOD.

12:33.211 --> 12:34.671
IT  WAS?

12:34.713 --> 12:35.714
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

12:35.754 --> 12:36.715
THEY'RE ASKING QUESTIONS!

12:36.755 --> 12:37.882
-YES!

12:37.924 --> 12:39.175
BUT NOBODY'S EVER ASKED

12:37.924 --> 12:39.175
QUESTIONS BEFORE.

12:39.217 --> 12:40.885
NOBODY'S EVEN

12:39.217 --> 12:40.885
PAID ATTENTION BEFORE.

12:40.927 --> 12:42.721
LOOK, JUST STICK

12:40.927 --> 12:42.721
TO THE TALKING POINTS.

12:42.761 --> 12:44.889
YOU'RE AN HONEST MAN

12:42.761 --> 12:44.889
WHO WANTS AN HONEST ECONOMY.

12:44.931 --> 12:47.308
IF YOU LOOK CONFIDENT,

12:44.931 --> 12:47.308
THEN YOU'LL  SOUND  CONFIDENT.

12:47.350 --> 12:48.685
HERE.

12:48.727 --> 12:50.103
ONCE THEY KNOW YOU,

12:48.727 --> 12:50.103
THEY WILL LOVE YOU,

12:50.144 --> 12:51.145
AND THAT'S THE TRUTH.

12:51.187 --> 12:52.647
Oh, get that!

12:56.150 --> 12:57.402
WHAT WAS THAT?

12:57.444 --> 12:58.986
WHAT?

12:59.028 --> 13:01.906
...THIS WOMAN THAT VITTORI

12:59.028 --> 13:01.906
IS SPEAKING WITH --

13:01.948 --> 13:04.325
IS SHE IN FACT INVOLVED

13:04.367 --> 13:06.911
WITH HIS CAMPAIGN...

13:15.128 --> 13:18.214
I'M HAPPY

13:15.128 --> 13:18.214
TO ANSWER QUESTIONS NOW.

13:18.256 --> 13:19.257
WHO IS THAT WOMAN?

13:19.299 --> 13:20.592
IS SHE YOUR GIRLFRIEND?

13:20.634 --> 13:22.719
EXCUSE ME.

13:20.634 --> 13:22.719
HOW IS THAT RELEVANT?

13:22.761 --> 13:25.179
WHAT ARE YOU TRYING TO HIDE?

13:25.221 --> 13:26.681
I'M NOT TRYING TO HIDE --

13:26.723 --> 13:30.268
DOES ANYONE HAVE A QUESTION

13:26.723 --> 13:30.268
RELATED TO MY CAMPAIGN?

13:30.310 --> 13:31.728
IS SHE A HOOKER?

13:31.770 --> 13:32.729
WHAT?!

13:32.771 --> 13:34.272
WHAT?!

13:34.314 --> 13:36.733
I AM AN HONEST MAN

13:36.775 --> 13:38.735
WHO WANTS AN HONEST ECONOMY.

13:38.777 --> 13:41.820
[ WATER BUBBLING ]

13:47.994 --> 13:50.121
[ BEEPING ]

13:54.459 --> 13:55.794
[ BEEP ]

13:55.834 --> 13:56.877
HELLO?

13:56.919 --> 13:57.920
General.

13:57.962 --> 13:59.422
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY ]

13:59.464 --> 14:01.132
ALWAYS FULL OF SURPRISES.

14:01.174 --> 14:03.384
WE'RE WORKING ON A WAY

14:01.174 --> 14:03.384
TO GET YOU OUT OF THERE, SIR.

14:03.426 --> 14:04.636
And my people?

14:04.678 --> 14:06.929
SPENCER, THE REST OF MY CABINET,

14:06.971 --> 14:09.140
MEN I FOUGHT WITH, MY MINISTERS,

14:09.182 --> 14:10.433
THEY'RE DOWN HERE WITH ME.

14:10.475 --> 14:12.143
I CAN'T LEAVE WITHOUT THEM.

14:12.185 --> 14:13.770
SIR, WE CAN BARELY FIND A WAY

14:13.812 --> 14:15.396
TO GET YOU OUT OF THERE ALONE.

14:15.438 --> 14:16.981
THESE PEOPLE YOU ARE WITH NOW --

14:17.023 --> 14:18.733
WOULD YOU LEAVE

14:17.023 --> 14:18.733
ANY OF THEM BEHIND?

14:18.775 --> 14:19.818
EVER?

14:23.321 --> 14:24.947
I thought so.

14:24.989 --> 14:26.366
I cannot take the chance

14:26.407 --> 14:28.451
THEY WILL KILL THESE MEN

14:26.407 --> 14:28.451
IN REPRISAL IF YOU RESCUE ME.

14:28.493 --> 14:30.077
Leave me here...

14:30.119 --> 14:32.121
NO MATTER WHAT.

14:32.163 --> 14:33.707
[ BEEP ]

14:35.333 --> 14:36.459
[ BEEP ]

14:36.501 --> 14:39.379
YOU OKAY?

14:41.964 --> 14:45.134
NATE, I HOPE YOU'RE HAVING

14:41.964 --> 14:45.134
A BETTER DAY THAN  WE  ARE.

14:45.176 --> 14:46.386
NOT EXACTLY.

14:46.427 --> 14:48.095
NATE, WE HAVE TO DO SOMETHING.

14:48.137 --> 14:49.930
NO, NO, NO. IF MOREAU FINDS OUT

14:48.137 --> 14:49.930
WE'RE IN THE COUNTRY,

14:49.972 --> 14:51.808
HE'S GONNA KILL -- SOPH--

14:51.850 --> 14:54.477
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:54.519 --> 14:56.521
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

14:56.563 --> 15:00.983
[ Latino accent ] UH, MY NAME

14:56.563 --> 15:00.983
IS, UH, REBECCA IBANEZ,

15:01.025 --> 15:04.278
AND...WELL, WE WERE TRYING

15:01.025 --> 15:04.278
TO KEEP THIS A BIG SECRET,

15:04.320 --> 15:06.823
BUT, YES, AS MICHAEL'S

15:04.320 --> 15:06.823
GRANDMOTHER USED TO SAY --

15:06.865 --> 15:09.325
"THE TRUTH IS A LIGHT,

15:06.865 --> 15:09.325
AND THE LIGHT MUST SHINE."

15:09.367 --> 15:12.453
WE'RE GETTING MARRIED!

15:09.367 --> 15:12.453
[ LAUGHS ]

15:12.495 --> 15:14.372
[ REPORTERS MURMURING ]

15:16.082 --> 15:17.667
My grandmother --

15:16.082 --> 15:17.667
she never said --

15:17.709 --> 15:19.544
[ LAUGHING ]

15:19.586 --> 15:21.962
YES. OH,

15:19.586 --> 15:21.962
IT'S VERY HAPPY NEWS, YES.

15:22.004 --> 15:24.340
HE'S A WONDERFUL MAN.

15:22.004 --> 15:24.340
[ CHUCKLES ]

15:26.593 --> 15:27.594
ONE AT A TIME.

15:27.635 --> 15:29.053
[ REPORTERS SHOUTING QUESTIONS ]

15:29.095 --> 15:31.723
YES, YES, I AM ALSO

15:29.095 --> 15:31.723
A SCHOOLTEACHER.

15:31.765 --> 15:33.641
I TEACH

15:31.765 --> 15:33.641
UNDERPRIVILEGED CHILDREN...

15:33.683 --> 15:35.852
HEY, MAN.

15:33.683 --> 15:35.852
HEY, THE FEEDBACK IS GREAT.

15:35.894 --> 15:37.854
I MEAN,

15:35.894 --> 15:37.854
ONLINE'S GOING CRAZY FOR HER.

15:37.896 --> 15:39.856
THERE'S A HASH TAG ON HER.

15:39.898 --> 15:41.315
THERE'S A BUNCH OF PHONE VIDEOS

15:39.898 --> 15:41.315
GOING VIRAL.

15:41.357 --> 15:42.859
WHAT ABOUT HER BACK STORY?

15:42.901 --> 15:45.361
I HAVE TO WAIT TILL SHE'S  DONE

15:42.901 --> 15:45.361
MAKING IT UP,

15:45.403 --> 15:47.947
BUT I CAN GRAFT ONE

15:45.403 --> 15:47.947
OF HER OLD I.D.s ONTO IT.

15:47.988 --> 15:50.366
LISTEN, MAN,

15:47.988 --> 15:50.366
SHE'S NOT PRINCESS DI.

15:50.408 --> 15:53.160
IT'S A SMALL COUNTRY.

15:50.408 --> 15:53.160
WE GOT THIS. WE --

15:53.202 --> 15:54.995
OH, HELL, IT'S MOREAU.

15:55.037 --> 15:56.748
YEAH, I CAUGHT THAT.

15:56.790 --> 15:58.332
-FORD.

15:56.790 --> 15:58.332
-YEAH.

15:58.374 --> 16:00.585
I HAVE TO ASK --

15:58.374 --> 16:00.585
WHY WON'T YOU LEAVE ME ALONE?

16:00.627 --> 16:02.169
WELL, YOU MOVE DIRTY MONEY.

16:02.211 --> 16:05.047
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

16:05.089 --> 16:07.759
WELL, WE WANT A BIG FAMILY.

16:07.801 --> 16:12.096
BEHIND EVERY GREAT FORTUNE,

16:07.801 --> 16:12.096
THERE IS A GREAT CRIME.

16:12.138 --> 16:15.266
IF WE COULDN'T MOVE MONEY

16:12.138 --> 16:15.266
JUST BECAUSE IT WAS DIRTY,

16:15.308 --> 16:17.226
THE WORLD ECONOMY

16:15.308 --> 16:17.226
WOULD COLLAPSE.

16:17.268 --> 16:19.729
I'M A BANKER, FORD.

16:19.771 --> 16:22.565
SOME BANKS BUY LAND.

16:19.771 --> 16:22.565
I BUY POLITICIANS.

16:22.607 --> 16:24.776
SOME BANKS INVEST IN BUSINESS.

16:24.818 --> 16:26.820
I INVEST IN COUNTRIES.

16:26.861 --> 16:28.404
AND I THINK  BIG,

16:28.446 --> 16:32.366
AND I DON'T JUDGE

16:28.446 --> 16:32.366
THE MEN I DO BUSINESS WITH.

16:32.408 --> 16:36.078
NOW, THAT'S NOT A SIN.

16:32.408 --> 16:36.078
THAT'S VISION.

16:36.120 --> 16:37.079
OH.

16:37.121 --> 16:38.456
-NOW, COME ALONG.

16:37.121 --> 16:38.456
-[ STAMMERS ]

16:38.498 --> 16:41.083
MY MAN HERE HAS HACKED

16:38.498 --> 16:41.083
INTO ALL THE SECURITY FEEDS

16:41.125 --> 16:42.543
IN THE PARLIAMENT BUILDING,

16:42.585 --> 16:45.045
SO IF ANYTHING WERE TO HAPPEN

16:42.585 --> 16:45.045
TO ME OR MY TEAM,

16:45.087 --> 16:48.132
THE FOOTAGE WOULD GO STRAIGHT

16:45.087 --> 16:48.132
TO THE POLICE AND TO INTERPOL.

16:48.174 --> 16:49.550
THAT'S NOT MY PROBLEM.

16:49.592 --> 16:51.260
WELL, I THINK

16:49.592 --> 16:51.260
YOU SHOULD KNOW, THOUGH,

16:51.302 --> 16:53.137
THAT THERE ARE MORE

16:51.302 --> 16:53.137
U.N. ELECTION OFFICIALS

16:53.179 --> 16:55.431
HERE IN THIS COUNTRY RIGHT NOW

16:53.179 --> 16:55.431
THAN THERE ARE TOURISTS.

16:55.473 --> 16:57.433
[ CHUCKLES ]

16:55.473 --> 16:57.433
NOW, YOUR MAN RIBERA,

16:57.475 --> 16:59.018
HE'S ALREADY ARRESTED

16:57.475 --> 16:59.018
HIS MAIN OPPONENT.

16:59.059 --> 17:00.937
SO IF ANYTHING FURTHER WERE

16:59.059 --> 17:00.937
TO GO WRONG WITH HIS ELECTION,

17:00.979 --> 17:05.274
LIKE, SAY, THE KIDNAPPING

17:00.979 --> 17:05.274
OF U.S. CITIZENS --

17:05.316 --> 17:09.111
WELL, YOU JUST MIGHT LOSE

17:05.316 --> 17:09.111
YOUR SAFE HAVEN.

17:11.238 --> 17:13.157
MAKE IT INTERESTING, FORD.

17:13.199 --> 17:15.493
YEAH, I'LL -- I'LL TRY.

17:17.996 --> 17:20.080
YOU  DO  KNOW

17:17.996 --> 17:20.080
I HAVEN'T HACKED INTO ANY

17:20.122 --> 17:22.041
OF THE SECURITY FEEDS

17:20.122 --> 17:22.041
FOR PARLIAMENT.

17:22.082 --> 17:23.250
YEAH.

17:23.292 --> 17:24.627
-I SHOULD GO GET ON THAT.

17:23.292 --> 17:24.627
-DO.

17:24.669 --> 17:25.795
YEAH.

17:27.588 --> 17:29.924
OH, BOY, SOPHIE,

17:27.588 --> 17:29.924
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

17:29.966 --> 17:32.760
HONEY, DON'T BE SO SHY.

17:29.966 --> 17:32.760
[ LAUGHS ]

17:37.015 --> 17:39.017
[ Chuckling ]

17:37.015 --> 17:39.017
HEY. UP 10 POINTS.

17:39.058 --> 17:40.267
NOT ENOUGH.

17:40.309 --> 17:41.853
[ BEEPING ]

17:41.895 --> 17:43.021
IT'S 10 POINTS, MAN.

17:41.895 --> 17:43.021
SOPHIE'S A HIT.

17:43.062 --> 17:45.648
IT'S NOT ENOUGH.

17:45.690 --> 17:48.526
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

17:53.113 --> 17:55.867
ELIOT, PARKER, START LOOKING

17:53.113 --> 17:55.867
AT THOSE OTHER PLANS.

17:55.909 --> 17:58.369
THOSE ARE PRETTY NASTY.

17:58.411 --> 17:59.871
WELCOME TO POLITICS.

18:04.458 --> 18:06.002
[ Sighing ] OKAY.

18:06.044 --> 18:07.795
I AM WORRIED, MR. DRAPER.

18:07.837 --> 18:09.505
I SHOULD NOT BE LYING

18:07.837 --> 18:09.505
TO THE PEOPLE.

18:09.547 --> 18:11.298
I AGREE.

18:09.547 --> 18:11.298
YOU KNOW, YOU'RE UP 10 POINTS.

18:11.340 --> 18:13.551
-I  AM?

18:11.340 --> 18:13.551
-MICHAEL...

18:13.593 --> 18:15.344
DO YOU BELIEVE THAT RIBERA

18:13.593 --> 18:15.344
IS BAD FOR THE PEOPLE?

18:15.386 --> 18:16.804
ABSOLUTELY.

18:16.846 --> 18:18.264
THEN IT'S WORTH ANYTHING

18:16.846 --> 18:18.264
TO STOP HIM. FOR THE PEOPLE!

18:18.305 --> 18:19.807
-I SUPPOSE...

18:18.305 --> 18:19.807
-DON'T THINK OF IT AS A LIE.

18:19.849 --> 18:22.351
THINK OF YOUR ENGAGEMENT TO

18:19.849 --> 18:22.351
REBECCA AS A CAMPAIGN PROMISE.

18:22.393 --> 18:23.644
YOU TELL PEOPLE

18:22.393 --> 18:23.644
YOU'RE GONNA MARRY HER,

18:23.686 --> 18:25.521
AND WHEN YOU BECOME PRESIDENT,

18:23.686 --> 18:25.521
MM, YOU DON'T.

18:25.563 --> 18:27.565
HOW IS A CAMPAIGN PROMISE

18:25.563 --> 18:27.565
DIFFERENT THAN A LIE?

18:27.607 --> 18:29.984
[ LAUGHS ]

18:27.607 --> 18:29.984
IT'S COMPLICATED.

18:30.026 --> 18:32.111
RIGHT NOW, YOUR PEOPLE,

18:30.026 --> 18:32.111
THEY NEED A PEP TALK.

18:32.152 --> 18:34.196
IT'S NOT ABOUT  US  ANYMORE.

18:32.152 --> 18:34.196
IT'S ABOUT  THEM.

18:34.238 --> 18:36.574
COME ON!

18:34.238 --> 18:36.574
LET'S GET STARTED!

18:36.616 --> 18:38.117
OKAY, WELL, AFTER TWO FULL DAYS,

18:36.616 --> 18:38.117
YOU'RE STILL ALIVE.

18:38.158 --> 18:41.412
MICHAEL WAS SECONDS AWAY

18:38.158 --> 18:41.412
FROM BURYING YOUR LITTLE PLAN

18:41.454 --> 18:42.413
IN A SHALLOW GRAVE.

18:42.455 --> 18:44.040
"SHALLOW GRAVE"?

18:42.455 --> 18:44.040
WELL, THAT'S GOOD.

18:44.082 --> 18:46.166
REMEMBER THAT JOKE NEXT TIME

18:44.082 --> 18:46.166
WE'RE IN THE FOREST

18:46.208 --> 18:47.627
WITH TWO SHOVELS IN OUR HANDS.

18:47.668 --> 18:49.045
COUNTRY OF 300,000 PEOPLE --

18:49.087 --> 18:50.630
HALF OF THEM LIKELY TO VOTE --

18:50.671 --> 18:52.882
YEAH, I JUST NEED 20,000

18:50.671 --> 18:52.882
OF THEM TO CHANGE THEIR MIND...

18:52.924 --> 18:54.050
IN LESS THAN A WEEK.

18:54.092 --> 18:57.177
NATE, IF STEALING

18:54.092 --> 18:57.177
A COUNTRY WERE EASY...

18:58.345 --> 18:59.430
